Hey, we heard you lost your password.

<% if @user && @user_token.valid? %>
	Use the following link within the next 24 hours to reset your password:
	<%= token_sessions_url(:host => @host, :account_name => Account.current.name, :token => @user_token.token) %>
<% elsif @user %>
	Unfortunately there was an error while attempting to reset your password.
	Please contact an administrator.
<% else %>
	Unfortunately we were unable to find your account with the username <%= @username %>.
<% end %>

Thanks,
The Omega Team
